description: Add artistic flair at home or on the go with the Terrain Watercolor Confections Set from Prima Marketing! This set of dreamy watercolor hues comes in a metal tin that measures 4.75″ x 2.75″. Included in the metal tin are 12 highly pigmented dry watercolors – just grab a brush and add water to bring these hues to life. The metal tin also includes two fold out mixing areas that you can create your own rich tones and colors on. Simply let your custom colors dry to use for later or wipe them up to clean your palette and make some new unique hues! You’ll love the earthy and geographical colors found in the Terrain set. They’re perfect for painting desert scenes, valleys, forests, sunrises, gardens, sunrises, and more. This set is part of the Watercolor Confections Collection by Prima Marketing. Included in the package is one metal tin with 12 dry watercolor pans.
name: Watercolor Confections Terrain

description: Create gorgeous scenes dressed in blue, purple, and green with the Currents Watercolor Confections watercolor painting set from Prima Marketing. This set includes 12 highly pigmented watercolors that quickly come to life with water. Grab up your favorite brush, a cup of water, and get creative at home or on the go. This set is 4.75″ x 2.75″, so you can easily take it anywhere you’re hoping to let off a little creative steam. This metal tin also includes two fold-out palettes for mixing your own variations of the rich, included colors. Simply let your unique hues dry to bring back to life later or wipe up the mixing areas when you’re finished to create more original tones. The Currents set has colors that are perfect for painting water scenes, forests, creeks, mermaids, magical places, and more!

description: Get the creamy look of oil with the practicality of watercolor when you use Water Soluble Oil Pastels from Art Philosophy by Prima Marketing! In the Basics Set, you’ll find 12 luscious colors that can be used dry or with water. Use these gorgeous pigments like dark ochre, cadmium green and Lavender Collection on a heavy weight or watercolor paper to create jaw-dropping backgrounds, drawings, artist effects, and more! This package contains all of the colors you need to mix your favorite tones and hues.
name: Watersoluble Oil Pastels Basics

description: Get the best of both worlds with the Rustic Set of Water Soluble Oil Pastels from Prima Marketing. This is a set of 12 luscious pastels from the Art Philosophy Collection. Why are these richly-pigmented pastels the best of both worlds? These pastels offer the creaminess of oil pastels, but are water soluble! Use them dry or grab up your favorite brush and add water for unique, dreamy effects. This set includes must-have hues like vermilion, prussian blue, salmon pink, and more. You will have a blast mixing and matching these neutrals and jewel tones to create drawings, backgrounds, abstract designs, and whatever your imagination inspires!
name: Watersoluble Oil Pastels Rustic
